gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n潮流野黎姐，同喇叭褲一樣"},{"pid":"fcfc7f31e5ea3aa430c59aabe8cf93e4ccc21d33","tid":2257474,"uid":316949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:01:40.000Z","msg":"好多實體報紙係比啲唔願意改變既藍絲廢老睇<br />\n事實上好多銀髮同後生都訂撚左蘋果日報<br />\n係咪真係需要日日製造咁多垃圾?<br />\n其他果啲果拎去五毫子一斤囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56e21ad3d438d8c9158f973568962fe13d4790d","tid":2257474,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dcb60a188e264d267cf1c5f55a5b3c8d9a77628","tid":2257474,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:03:28.000Z","msg":"一早訂晒網上版啦"},{"pid":"cabc0ec016ac04b95a4ce7f5d11f4e11ed020a48","tid":2257474,"uid":316949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dcb60a188e264d267cf1c5f55a5b3c8d9a77628","tid":2257474,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:03:28.000Z","msg":"一早訂晒網上版啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:05:48.000Z","msg":"建議海外巴絲or移民既港人<br />\n以後想關注香港時事,可以網上訂閱蘋果<br />\n依家咩年代,佢地以後想睇報紙或支持呢間報社都唔親自落街買<br />\n某啲特定既活動/行動除外"},{"pid":"38095d7a450f046fae5f68088c0b480ade96f11d","tid":2257474,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:06:21.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦，長貧難顧"},{"pid":"d986312e82c932e58e95be6853cc3bdac7382a1a","tid":2257474,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:07:49.000Z","msg":"應該假期朝早買份俾屋企老嘢睇"},{"pid":"8f630280a2d9bc61cef09eb61a8054a895520e30","tid":2257474,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:18:51.000Z","msg":"一向都覺得買報紙係冇咩意思<br />\n真係所謂嘅有畫面（可以打下卡咁）<br />\n就你影張相而言<br />\nok便利店本身係藍<br />\n再加上分銷商同運輸公司又唔一定係黃<br />\n有幾多錢落到蘋果袋呢？<br />\n<br />\n所以有銀髮買蘋果支持<br />\n我都會叫佢地升級vip好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}